title: First lady's girls' education effort gets Pakistani boost
text:
> Political First lady's girls' education effort gets Pakistani boost First lady Michelle Obama speak during an event in the Blue Room of the White House in Washington, Thursday, Oct. 22, 2015. Mrs. Obama announced a new partnership to further adolescent girls' education in Pakistan as a part of the Let Girls Learn initiative that aims to help adolescent girls around the globe attend and complete school.
